<body>

<!-- -------------------- Title & description -------------------- -->
<h1>Circles &amp; Triangles</h1>
<p>
    Circles have 360&nbsp;degrees of arc.  An inscribed angle (drawn on the circle)
    always measures exactly one&nbsp;half of the central angle that subtends the
    same arc.  Use the sliders or drag the vertices to explore the relationships.
</p>

<!-- -------------------- Canvas & info panel -------------------- -->
<div id="main-container">

    <!-- p5.js will insert its &lt;canvas&gt; here -->
    <div id="canvas-container"></div>

    <!-- info panel -->
